2025-03-31 21:42:56.207 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (7ms) [Parameters=[@__roles_0='?' (Size = 4000), @__normalizedPagePath_1='?' (Size = 4000), @__simplifiedPath_2='?' (Size = 4000)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT TOP(1) [r].[CanAccess]
FROM [RolePermissions] AS [r]
WHERE [r].[RoleName] IN (

2025-03-31 21:44:45.647 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (6ms) [Parameters=[@__roles_0='?' (Size = 4000), @__normalizedPagePath_1='?' (Size = 4000), @__simplifiedPath_2='?' (Size = 4000)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT TOP(1) [r].[CanAccess]
FROM [RolePermissions] AS [r]
WHERE [r].[RoleName] IN (
    SELECT [r0].[value]
    FROM OPENJSON(@__roles_0) WITH ([value] nvarchar(max) '$') AS [r0]
